# Ariadne Decision: Business Detail MVP Behavior (2026-04-18)

## Context
Completing todo `build-business-detail` for narrowed MVP scope (no visit tracking, minimal business model).

## Decision
Business detail screen will:
- Show only MVP business fields: `name`, `category`, `address`, and `lat/lng` coordinates.
- Include an embedded map snippet with a single marker at the business coordinates when `GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY` is configured.
- Show a friendly non-crashing fallback message when the map key is missing.
- Provide a "View on Google Maps" button using a coordinate-based deep link (`https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=lat,lng`).

## Navigation Contract
List and map entry points both navigate to the same detail screen implementation so behavior stays consistent regardless of where selection originates.

## Rationale
This preserves MVP scope while delivering practical detail usability and resilience under incomplete env configuration.
